n但近排太受刺激 啲情緒出晒嚟，人人都厭我煩<br />\n一靜落嚟就唔開心，唔識開心返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想發泄控制唔到"},{"pid":"f833e570df371c4ed0511107f6d704e14ed7c23c","tid":685282,"uid":143443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f33b8162286c485a372879f3ff2fb97b92e40d4","tid":685282,"uid":93802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"我都你一樣，對住人好開心，得自己一個就充滿負能量，成日喊，成日覺得人地欠左我，甚至 我有一日都好想自殺。後來，我意識到自己咁樣唔係好點，我同好多人傾，其實佢地最多都係關心下你。解決既方法要解開你煩惱緊D咩，同埋俾正能量自己，我每星期定立一個小目標俾自己，從而令自己有返D動力過生活。記住呀絲打，你同咩人傾都無用，最緊要你要有幫自己既決心。加油！"},{"pid":"9985fd9fe38b56c61762fd994bfbf9e25e21cb98","tid":685282,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"喂I&rsquo;m here 乜都可以同我講<br />\n我唔mean架其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63f2b9db6f2c470b7a1964bdb4cf70fdb8160a0","tid":685282,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a581f76bdabe74bf57d19b60c439d83f164ab8","tid":685282,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad51eab2e0e55bcb066fc818a3a0822af29140f3","tid":685282,"uid":116942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"煩9 ME is ok， 最鍾意幫人solve problem <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}